[
  {
    "startTime": 0.0,
    "endTime": 2.0,
    "text": "Hold up, I'll walk you out."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.0,
    "endTime": 4.0,
    "text": "Hold up, what's going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 4.0,
    "endTime": 6.0,
    "text": "I can't believe she basically offered me a job."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.0,
    "endTime": 7.0,
    "text": "I know!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.0,
    "endTime": 8.0,
    "text": "I'm going home!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 8.0,
    "endTime": 9.0,
    "text": "Fine, then I'm going with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.0,
    "endTime": 12.0,
    "text": "Boss!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "What is this about?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.0,
    "endTime": 16.0,
    "text": "Nothing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.0,
    "endTime": 18.0,
    "text": "Everything!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.0,
    "endTime": 20.0,
    "text": "I don't know, it's..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.0,
    "endTime": 22.0,
    "text": "I don't think I actually do want to run the shop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "I'm trapped."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.0,
    "endTime": 25.0,
    "text": "Amber!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 26.0,
    "endTime": 27.0,
    "text": "Don't move!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.0,
    "endTime": 29.0,
    "text": "Please, my mother."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.0,
    "endTime": 32.0,
    "text": "Mom, it's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.0,
    "endTime": 33.0,
    "text": "He's just a friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.0,
    "endTime": 34.0,
    "text": "Sai!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.0,
    "endTime": 36.0,
    "text": "Silence!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.0,
    "endTime": 43.0,
    "text": "If your father find out, fire and water cannot be together."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.0,
    "endTime": 46.0,
    "text": "I splash this on your heart to bring love to the surface."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.0,
    "endTime": 51.0,
    "text": "And I read the smoke."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.0,
    "endTime": 63.0,
    "text": "What are you doing?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.0,
    "endTime": 69.0,
    "text": "My dad!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.0,
    "endTime": 70.0,
    "text": "You have to go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 72.0,
    "endTime": 74.0,
    "text": "Wait, are we a match?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.0,
    "endTime": 75.0,
    "text": "What's going on?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.0,
    "endTime": 79.0,
    "text": "I was going to tell you tomorrow, but I'm too excited to sleep."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.0,
    "endTime": 82.0,
    "text": "In two days, I retire!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.0,
    "endTime": 89.0,
    "text": "When I left Fireland, I gave my father the Box Soul."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.0,
    "endTime": 92.0,
    "text": "It is the highest form of respect."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.0,
    "endTime": 96.0,
    "text": "But my father did not return the bow."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.0,
    "endTime": 100.0,
    "text": "He say, if we leave Fireland, we will lose who we are."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.0,
    "endTime": 105.0,
    "text": "He didn't get to see that I never forgot we are firemen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.0,
    "endTime": 110.0,
    "text": "It is important that you know you have my blessing every day."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.0,
    "endTime": 111.0,
    "text": "You need your rest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.0,
    "endTime": 118.0,
    "text": "Amber, what did your mom say about our reading?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.0,
    "endTime": 119.0,
    "text": "Nothing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.0,
    "endTime": 122.0,
    "text": "Wait, I have something to show you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.0,
    "endTime": 125.0,
    "text": "Give me two seconds, and you'll need a pair of boots."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.0,
    "endTime": 130.0,
    "text": "Why do we have these?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 131.0,
    "text": "Who knows?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.0,
    "endTime": 135.0,
    "text": "Hey, it's my favorite fireball."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 135.0,
    "endTime": 139.0,
    "text": "That flooded tunnel goes to the main terminal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.0,
    "endTime": 140.0,
    "text": "Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.0,
    "endTime": 142.0,
    "text": "Do you still want to see a vivisteria?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.0,
    "endTime": 145.0,
    "text": "Wait, I'm supposed to get in there?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.0,
    "endTime": 146.0,
    "text": "The air should last..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.0,
    "endTime": 147.0,
    "text": "At least 20 minutes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 148.0,
    "endTime": 151.0,
    "text": "Why does anyone get to tell you what you can do in your life?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.0,
    "endTime": 162.0,
    "text": "Whoa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.0,
    "endTime": 175.0,
    "text": "Oh, my."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.0,
    "endTime": 184.0,
    "text": "Hey, you're running out of air."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 188.0,
    "endTime": 195.0,
    "text": "I'm so sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.0,
    "endTime": 196.0,
    "text": "I should never..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.0,
    "endTime": 197.0,
    "text": "Are you kidding?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.0,
    "endTime": 198.0,
    "text": "That was amazing!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.0,
    "endTime": 200.0,
    "text": "I finally saw a vivisteria!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Can't we just prove it?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.0,
    "endTime": 203.0,
    "text": "Prove what?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.0,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": "Let's see what happens."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 206.0,
    "text": "I could vaporize you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.0,
    "endTime": 208.0,
    "text": "You could extinguish me, and then..."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.0,
    "endTime": 213.0,
    "text": "Let's start small."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.0,
    "endTime": 242.0,
    "text": "Yeah, that may work in your rich-kid-follow-your-heart family, but getting to do what you want is a luxury, and not for people like me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.0,
    "endTime": 243.0,
    "text": "Funny."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.0,
    "endTime": 249.0,
    "text": "This whole time, I thought you were so strong, but it turns out you're just afraid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 249.0,
    "endTime": 250.0,
    "text": "I'm fire, Wade!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.0,
    "endTime": 254.0,
    "text": "I can't be anything more than that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.0,
    "endTime": 256.0,
    "text": "It's what I am and what my family is."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.0,
    "endTime": 259.0,
    "text": "And that alone is a reason this could never work."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.0,
    "endTime": 260.0,
    "text": "It's over, Wade."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.0,
    "endTime": 262.0,
    "text": "Fire Town!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.0,
    "endTime": 276.0,
    "text": "Well, one-way tickets anywhere but here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.0,
    "endTime": 278.0,
    "text": "I made you a painting."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 278.0,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "It's of a lonely man awash in sadness."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 282.0,
    "text": "Flash flood!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.0,
    "endTime": 283.0,
    "text": "Hurry!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.0,
    "endTime": 284.0,
    "text": "Water!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.0,
    "endTime": 301.0,
    "text": "Get to higher ground!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 302.0,
    "text": "Bernie!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.0,
    "endTime": 303.0,
    "text": "Wade?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.0,
    "endTime": 303.0,
    "text": "Mom!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.0,
    "endTime": 303.0,
    "text": "Wade?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.0,
    "endTime": 303.0,
    "text": "Yee-haw!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.0,
    "endTime": 319.0,
    "text": "Pull the door!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.0,
    "endTime": 339.0,
    "text": "No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.0,
    "endTime": 340.0,
    "text": "We have to go!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.0,
    "endTime": 341.0,
    "text": "We have to go now!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.0,
    "endTime": 342.0,
    "text": "I can't leave!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.0,
    "endTime": 345.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry to say this, but the shop is done!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.0,
    "endTime": 346.0,
    "text": "Oh, Wade."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.0,
    "endTime": 347.0,
    "text": "Thank you, thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 349.0,
    "endTime": 361.0,
    "text": "It's too hot in here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 361.0,
    "endTime": 371.0,
    "text": "I don't know what to do!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.0,
    "endTime": 377.0,
    "text": "It's okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.0,
    "endTime": 378.0,
    "text": "No, it's not okay!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 379.0,
    "endTime": 380.0,
    "text": "Ember, I have no regrets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.0,
    "endTime": 387.0,
    "text": "You gave me something people search for their whole lives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.0,
    "endTime": 391.0,
    "text": "I really do love it when your light does that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.0,
    "endTime": 392.0,
    "text": "We're in the heart!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.0,
    "endTime": 405.0,
    "text": "I needed to tell you the truth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.0,
    "endTime": 408.0,
    "text": "I don't want to run the shop."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.0,
    "endTime": 409.0,
    "text": "I'm sorry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.0,
    "endTime": 410.0,
    "text": "I'm a bad daughter."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.0,
    "endTime": 414.0,
    "text": "The shop was never the dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 417.0,
    "endTime": 418.0,
    "text": "You were the dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 418.0,
    "endTime": 421.0,
    "text": "You were always the dream."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 421.0,
    "endTime": 421.0,
    "text": "No!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.0,
    "endTime": 438.0,
    "text": "I want to explore the world with you, Wade Redbolt!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.0,
    "endTime": 439.0,
    "text": "I knew it!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.0,
    "endTime": 458.0,
    "text": "My nose always knows!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.0,
    "endTime": 466.0,
    "text": "You know, I'm not really one for tearful goodbyes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.0,
    "endTime": 466.0,
    "text": "Oh, Wade!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.0,
    "endTime": 467.0,
    "text": "You big liar!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.0,
    "endTime": 474.0,
    "text": "Dad, I'm sorry the internship is so far away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474.0,
    "endTime": 478.0,
    "text": "I mean, it's the best glass design company in the world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.0,
    "endTime": 478.0,
    "text": "Yeah, shh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.0,
    "endTime": 478.0,
    "text": "Go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.0,
    "endTime": 479.0,
    "text": "Start new life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 479.0,
    "endTime": 482.0,
    "text": "Your mother and I will be here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 482.0,
    "endTime": 483.0,
    "text": " I love you."
  }
]